                        <article id="post-681" class="post-681 page type-page status-publish hentry">
                            <div class="entry-content">
                                <h1 style="text-align: center;">ICS 169 A &amp; B: CGS Capstone</h1>
<h6 style="text-align: center;">Computer Game Science Major &#8211;¬†Fall &amp; Winter 2016-2017</h6>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Professor Joshua Tanenbaum</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">Email: <a href="mailto:joshua.tanenbaum@uci.edu">joshua.tanenbaum@uci.edu</a></p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Teaching Assistant:¬†Calvin Liu</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">Email: <a href="mailto:CalvinLiu20503@gmail.com" target="_blank">CalvinLiu20503@gmail.com</a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Tu, Thur, 11:00am ‚Äì 12:20pm</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Location: SSL 270¬†<em><strong>(and various other locations &#8211; see schedule below)</strong></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Office Hours: By appointment</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Course Website:¬†<a href="https://transformativeplay.ics.uci.edu/classes/ics-169-capstone/">https://transformativeplay.ics.uci.edu/classes/ics-169-capstone/</a></p>
<table width="600">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="border: 2px solid #000000; text-align: center;" colspan="6" width="600">Quick Menu</td>
